# TaskFlow — Complete Deployment Plan

> **Stack Summary**
> | Layer | Technology | Deploy Target |
> |---|---|---|
> | Backend | Node.js · Express · MySQL · Socket.IO | **Render** (free tier) |
> | Web Frontend | React 18 · Vite | **Vercel** (free tier) |
> | Mobile App | React Native · Expo SDK 52 | **Expo Go** / **EAS Build** |
> | Database | MySQL 8 | **Aiven** (free tier) |
> | Email | Mailtrap SDK | Mailtrap cloud |

---

## Phase 1 — Pre-Deployment Checklist

Before anything is deployed, make sure all of the following are true locally.

### 1.1 — Verify the Backend Runs Locally

```bash
cd "d:\Developments\College Project\taskflow-backend"
npm install
npm run migrate        # runs DB migrations
npm start              # should print: [TaskFlow] Server running on port 5000
```

Open `http://localhost:5000/api/health` (or any existing route) and confirm you get a valid JSON response.

### 1.2 — Verify the Frontend Runs Locally

```bash
cd "d:\Developments\College Project\taskflow-app"
npm install
npm run dev            # should open on http://localhost:5173
```

Log in, open the Dashboard, and confirm tasks, notifications, and real-time updates work.

### 1.3 — Verify the Mobile App Runs Locally

```bash
cd "d:\Developments\College Project\taskflow-mobile"
npm install
npx expo start         # scan QR with Expo Go app on your phone
```

Log in and confirm all screens load without errors.

### 1.4 — Run the Test Suite

```bash
cd "d:\Developments\College Project\taskflow-backend"
npm test               # must show 0 failing tests before you deploy
```

> [!CAUTION]
> **Do NOT deploy if any tests are failing.** Fix them first — a broken test means broken production behaviour.

### 1.5 — Clean Up Sensitive Files

- Make sure **[.env](file:///d:/Developments/College%20Project/taskflow-backend/.env) is listed in [.gitignore](file:///d:/Developments/College%20Project/.gitignore)** — never commit it.
- Make sure [backend-log.txt](file:///d:/Developments/College%20Project/taskflow-backend/backend-log.txt), [crash.log](file:///d:/Developments/College%20Project/taskflow-backend/crash.log), and `test-results*.txt` are also gitignored.

